data.description: Priced to sell! 7k towards closing!!    Agents, bring your clients by to view this gorgeous 2story home located by the historic Woodlawn Lake area. When entering the home, you'll be greeted by the beautiful open floor plan where the natural wood flooring flows throughout the first floor. Enjoy the welcoming kitchen, which has custom cabinets & lovely high-end quartz countertops. The Master suite is located on the first level, which offers a luxurious bathroom & walk-in closet. The utility room and half bath are also located on the first level. Take the wooden planked staircase up to the second floor where you'll be invited to the beautiful Jack & Jill bathroom layout. Home has a 2-car detached garage! This Lot has generous backyard with a deck to accommodate any occasion throughout the year. Thank you in advance for showing.
